Titolo: Art of Balance

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Art of Balance (stylized as art of balance) is a physics-based puzzle video game developed and published by Shin'en Multimedia. The game was originally released on WiiWare in 2010, then enhanced in high definition and ported to the Wii U's eShop in 2013, PlayStation 4 in 2016 and to Nintendo Switch in 2018. A version with touch controls was also ported to the Nintendo 3DS's eShop in 2012, titled Art of Balance TOUCH!

Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: 84
